==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thankworthy
<hw>Thank"wor`thy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Deserving
thanks; worthy of gratitude; mreitorious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>For this <qex>thankworthy</qex>, if a man, for conscience toward
God, endure grief, suffering wrongfully.</q> <rj><qau>1 Pet. ii.
19.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thar</ent>⟦br⟧
